  "sentences": {
    "01773816-5f49-4509-88fc-bc7e0fde6461": {
      "id": "01773816-5f49-4509-88fc-bc7e0fde6461",
      "transcriptId": "84e0dedc-37aa-4ddf-9d95-fbc88c1f1ba9",
      "speakerName": "张总",
      "speakerIndex": 0,
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 3.5,
      "content": "大家好，欢迎参加今天的采访。首先介绍一下我们公司最新的发展情况。",
      "wordCount": 1,
      "isSensitive": false,
      "sensitiveCategories": [],
      "sortOrder": 0,
      "createdAt": 1782086564107,
      "updatedAt": 1782086564107
    },
    "0db054ed-6a75-4230-9b58-ca5bd9521d46": {
      "id": "0db054ed-6a75-4230-9b58-ca5bd9521d46",
      "transcriptId": "84e0dedc-37aa-4ddf-9d95-fbc88c1f1ba9",
      "speakerName": "李记者",
      "speakerIndex": 1,
      "startTime": 3,
      "endTime": 6.5,
      "content": "张总您好，很高兴有这个机会。首先想请问一下，贵公司今年的营收目标是多少？",
      "wordCount": 1,
      "isSensitive": true,
      "sensitiveCategories": [
        "financial"
      ],
      "sortOrder": 1,
      "createdAt": 1782086564107,
      "updatedAt": 1782086564107
    },
    "ba6aa356-8ef9-44ba-be50-1999c1ee4cac": {
      "id": "ba6aa356-8ef9-44ba-be50-1999c1ee4cac",
      "transcriptId": "84e0dedc-37aa-4ddf-9d95-fbc88c1f1ba9",
      "speakerName": "张总",
      "speakerIndex": 0,
      "startTime": 6,
      "endTime": 9.5,
      "content": "关于财务数字方面，我们今年的目标是营收增长30%，达到五十亿的规模。具体的净利润数据还需要看下半年的表现。",
      "wordCount": 1,
      "isSensitive": true,
      "sensitiveCategories": [
        "financial"
      ],
      "sortOrder": 2,
      "createdAt": 1782086564107,
      "updatedAt": 1782086564107
    },
    "85b53ba9-eb40-4e08-9210-5200ea7104de": {
      "id": "85b53ba9-eb40-4e08-9210-5200ea7104de",
      "transcriptId": "84e0dedc-37aa-4ddf-9d95-fbc88c1f1ba9",
      "speakerName": "李记者",
      "speakerIndex": 1,
      "startTime": 10,
      "endTime": 13.5,
      "content": "了解了。那在产品方面，有没有什么新的动向可以透露？比如产品X的进展如何？",
      "wordCount": 1,
      "isSensitive": true,
      "sensitiveCategories": [
        "unreleased_product"
      ],
      "sortOrder": 3,
      "createdAt": 1782086564107,
      "updatedAt": 1782086564107
    },
    "1c50b2c5-db24-4bad-8dd4-73599976677c": {
      "id": "1c50b2c5-db24-4bad-8dd4-73599976677c",
      "transcriptId": "84e0dedc-37aa-4ddf-9d95-fbc88c1f1ba9",
      "speakerName": "张总",
      "speakerIndex": 0,
      "startTime": 14,
      "endTime": 17.5,
      "content": "产品X是我们正在研发的下一代产品，目前还属于未公开的状态，请暂时不要报道这部分内容。",
      "wordCount": 1,
      "isSensitive": true,
      "sensitiveCategories": [
        "unreleased_product",
        "legal"
      ],
      "sortOrder": 4,
      "createdAt": 1782086564107,
      "updatedAt": 1782086564107
    },
    "65ad04a3-80ff-4d43-910a-9ac3ef661e1a": {
      "id": "65ad04a3-80ff-4d43-910a-9ac3ef661e1a",
      "transcriptId": "84e0dedc-37aa-4ddf-9d95-fbc88c1f1ba9",
      "speakerName": "李记者",
      "speakerIndex": 1,
      "startTime": 18,
      "endTime": 21.5,
      "content": "好的，我明白了。那可以谈谈你们和重要客户的合作情况吗？比如客户A那边的项目进展。",
      "wordCount": 1,
      "isSensitive": true,
      "sensitiveCategories": [
        "customer_name"
      ],
      "sortOrder": 5,
      "createdAt": 1782086564107,
      "updatedAt": 1782086564107
    },
    "6a1b1734-3dae-44d6-b8d5-d7d7f07e997c": {
      "id": "6a1b1734-3dae-44d6-b8d5-d7d7f07e997c",
      "transcriptId": "84e0dedc-37aa-4ddf-9d95-fbc88c1f1ba9",
      "speakerName": "张总",
      "speakerIndex": 0,
      "startTime": 22,
      "endTime": 25.5,
      "content": "客户A是我们的战略客户之一，目前合作进展顺利。不过具体的项目细节涉及保密，不方便透露太多。",
      "wordCount": 1,
      "isSensitive": true,
      "sensitiveCategories": [
        "customer_name",
        "legal"
      ],
      "sortOrder": 6,
      "createdAt": 1782086564107,
